# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:153
translate spanish hwb_s01_4ada47e6:

    # "Isn’t?"
    "¿Despejada?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:159
translate spanish hwb_s01_2cdf1a0c:

    # "I slam on the brakes, their shriek piercing my ears. A glance at my rearview mirror shows a girl cringing next to an ancient looking car, covering her ears as I screech down the road."
    "Piso el freno de golpe, su chirrido me perfora los oídos. Un vistazo al espejo retrovisor muestra a una chica encogida junto a un coche de aspecto antiguo, tapándose los oídos mientras freno con estrépito."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:161
translate spanish hwb_s01_a63692ad:

    # "Making a U-turn of dubious legality, I pull up in front of her car, killing the motorhome’s engine."
    "Hago un giro en U de dudosa legalidad y me detengo frente a su coche, apagando el motor de la casa rodante."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:198
translate spanish hwb_s01_dbc1aaf5:

    # "I hop out and shield my eyes from the blazing New Mexico sun. Only now do I realize how precious the AC really is."
    "Salto fuera y me protejo los ojos del abrasador sol de Nuevo México. Solo ahora me doy cuenta de lo valioso que era el aire acondicionado."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:211
translate spanish hwb_s01_6036f7b5:

    # "It doesn’t take more than several steps before the girl comes bouncing up to me with a look of relief."
    "No doy más de unos pasos antes de que la chica venga saltando hacia mí con una expresión de alivio."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:229
translate spanish hwb_s01_977bf185:

    # Girl "Oh my god, thank you thank you thank you thank you! I was starting to think no one would ever stop!"
    Girl "О боже мой, спасибо, спасибо, спасибо! Я уж думала, никто никогда не остановится!"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:238
translate spanish hwb_s01_b6ebea6f:

    # "With each word she gets a little closer, until we’re finally within touching distance of each other, her smiling face now filling my entire field of vision."
    "Con cada palabra se acerca un poco más, hasta que finalmente estamos a una distancia de tocarnos, su rostro sonriente llenando ahora todo mi campo de visión."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:249
translate spanish hwb_s01_6677ec8b:

    # "Her bright auburn hair is done into a girlish sidetail, glistening beneath specks of sweat. Standing out in the heat has made her round, pale cheeks a sun kissed red. But she still looks put together, like the desert would sooner melt her than do any real damage to her looks."
    "Su brillante cabello caoba está recogido en una cola lateral juvenil, brillando entre gotas de sudor. Estar bajo el calor ha vuelto sus mejillas redondas y pálidas de un rojo besado por el sol. Pero aún así luce arreglada, como si el desierto se derritiera antes que causarle un daño real a su apariencia."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:258
translate spanish hwb_s01_9156e602:

    # "I almost feel embarrassed to be in front of someone who dresses so cute, her frilly yellow top and skirt putting my red t-shirt and khakis to shame."
    "Casi me siento avergonzada de estar frente a alguien que viste tan lindo, su blusa amarilla con volantes y falda hacen que mi camiseta roja y mis caquis parezcan una vergüenza."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:267
translate spanish hwb_s01_bce0300f:

    # "It’s all brought together by one thing, though. Her eyes. They’re blue—vividly blue, deep and rich, complementing the traces of her misty perfume as she gets closer and closer."
    "Pero todo se une por una cosa. Sus ojos. Son azules—vívidamente azules, profundos y ricos, complementando los rastros de su perfume brumoso mientras se acerca más y más."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:276
translate spanish hwb_s01_438eaf9a:

    # "Too close too close too close."
    "Demasiado cerca, demasiado cerca, demasiado cerca."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:286
translate spanish hwb_s01_685a6a9e:

    # "I scramble back and cough, trying to hide any awkwardness."
    "Retrocedo de golpe y toso, tratando de ocultar cualquier incomodidad."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:290
translate spanish hwb_s01_adcff037:

    # Amber "{cps=50}N-{w=0.7}No problem.{/cps}"
    Amber "{cps=50}Н{/cps}{cps=1}-{/cps}{cps=50}нет проблем.{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:322
translate spanish hwb_s01_8fdf252b:

    # "What’s she doing out here alone? Driving through? Hell, is she even alone?"
    "¿Qué hace ella aquí sola? ¿De paso? Demonios, ¿acaso está sola?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:324
translate spanish hwb_s01_6ac30979:

    # "I peer off into the plains on the side of the road, half expecting a guy to pop up from his hiding place now that some idiot has fallen for their trap."
    "Miro hacia las llanuras al costado de la carretera, medio esperando que un tipo salga de su escondite ahora que alguna idiota ha caído en su trampa."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:326
translate spanish hwb_s01_f48da80e:

    # "That idiot being me, of course."
    "Esa idiota soy yo, por supuesto."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:328
translate spanish hwb_s01_d9619c0f:

    # "But, much to my surprise, no one does. Instead, the girl continues to stare at me, smiling as she patiently waits for my response."
    "Pero, para mi sorpresa, no aparece nadie. En cambio, la chica sigue mirándome, sonriendo mientras espera pacientemente mi respuesta."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:330
translate spanish hwb_s01_b89d21f4:

    # "I glance behind her, focusing on her car."
    "Miro detrás de ella, enfocándome en su coche."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:332
translate spanish hwb_s01_7d8543e9:

    # Amber "So, what’s the issue? Your car break down?"
    Amber "Так что случилось? Твоя машина сломалась?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:334
translate spanish hwb_s01_4e548165:

    # Girl "I think so, yeah."
    Girl "Похоже на то."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:336
translate spanish hwb_s01_3b9bf767:

    # Girl "I was driving and it just kind of…"
    Girl "Я ехала, и потом она просто..."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:338
translate spanish hwb_s01_07c5bad6:

    # Amber "Stopped?"
    Amber "Остановилась?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:340
translate spanish hwb_s01_6c8ede54:

    # Girl "Yeah…"
    Girl "Ага..."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:342
translate spanish hwb_s01_99a615da:

    # "She lowers her head in shame, eyes fixated on her feet, kicking the dust around her."
    "Baja la cabeza con vergüenza, con la mirada fija en sus pies, pateando el polvo a su alrededor."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:344
translate spanish hwb_s01_e4a89227:

    # Amber "I'm not much of a car buff, but I can take a look at it."
    Amber "Я не эксперт в машинах, но могу глянуть твою."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:346
translate spanish hwb_s01_13fbe8bd:

    # "Her head pops back up and life returns to her eyes."
    "Su cabeza vuelve a levantarse y la vida regresa a sus ojos."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:348
translate spanish hwb_s01_ec19f52a:

    # Girl "Oh wow, could you?"
    Girl "Ух ты, правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:350
translate spanish hwb_s01_310a07fc:

    # Amber "Yeah. Can’t promise that I can do anything, but I can at least check it out."
    Amber "Конечно. Не обещаю, что оживлю ее, но взглянуть стоит."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:352
translate spanish hwb_s01_f94d5ea0:

    # Girl "That’d be great!"
    Girl "Было бы здорово!"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:388
translate spanish hwb_s01_f3ed6960:

    # Amber "Alright, first things first, then."
    Amber "Так, значит, начнем с самого важного."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:390
translate spanish hwb_s01_a7be15c3:

    # "This thing looks even older than my motorhome. It was probably a nice car once upon a time, but with a dented grill, multiple scratches, and faded murky green color, it’s hard to believe such a cute girl was driving it."
    "Esta cosa parece incluso más vieja que mi casa rodante. Probablemente fue un buen auto en algún momento, pero con la parrilla abollada, múltiples rayones y el color verde turbio descolorido, es difícil creer que una chica tan linda lo estuviera manejando."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:394
translate spanish hwb_s01_a351ba98:

    # "I slide into the fabric seat and start the ignition. I don’t know too much about how this stuff works, just enough to keep the motorhome from giving out, but I can’t imagine it’s too significant of an issue. Probably just a dead battery or—"
    "Me deslizo en el asiento de tela y enciendo el motor. No sé mucho sobre cómo funciona esto, solo lo suficiente para evitar que la casa rodante se descomponga, pero no imagino que sea un problema muy grave. Probablemente solo una batería muerta o..."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:405
translate spanish hwb_s01_83b18721:

    # "No gas."
    "Sin gasolina."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:407
translate spanish hwb_s01_75054de2:

    # "A single car passes by, cooling us with a refreshing gust of wind, sprinkled with dirt and sand."
    "Un solo auto pasa, refrescándonos con una ráfaga de viento revitalizante, salpicada de tierra y arena."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:411
translate spanish hwb_s01_6ec99e9d:

    # Girl "I-Is something wrong?"
    Girl "Чт-... Что-то не так?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:415
translate spanish hwb_s01_fecc2090:

    # "Is this a joke?"
    "¿Es broma?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:417
translate spanish hwb_s01_e57bef32:

    # Girl "Oh no! Did I break it?"
    Girl "О, нет! Я сломала ее?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:421
translate spanish hwb_s01_57d6a658:

    # Amber "Uhh, no, it’s just out of gas."
    Amber "Эмм, нет, просто бензин кончился."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:425
translate spanish hwb_s01_b2b09a28:

    # Girl "What, no way!"
    Girl "Да ну, не может быть!"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:429
translate spanish hwb_s01_16d4bd66:

    # Girl "Dad said I should've filled up before I left…"
    Girl "Говорил же папа заправиться перед отъездом..."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:431
translate spanish hwb_s01_421e2942:

    # "Is she for real? Why is this girl in the middle of nowhere by herself?"
    "¿Habla en serio? ¿Por qué esta chica está en medio de la nada sola?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:433
translate spanish hwb_s01_43f9acb4:

    # "As if trying to force all the ideas into the center of her brain, the girl grabs her head and whines under her breath."
    "Como si intentara forzar todas las ideas al centro de su cerebro, la chica se agarra la cabeza y gime en voz baja."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:437
translate spanish hwb_s01_cc84d6cc:

    # Girl "Ah man, and I didn’t charge my phone, either. What am I gonna do?"
    Girl "Блиин, я и телефон не зарядила. Что же мне делать?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:439
translate spanish hwb_s01_105062c5:

    # "I’d offer her mine, but I’ve never had a cellphone in my life."
    "Le ofrecería el mío, pero nunca he tenido un teléfono celular en mi vida."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:441
translate spanish hwb_s01_14d27864:

    # "Seems like you'd have to pretty absentminded to forget that, though."
    "Parece que tendrías que ser bastante despistada para olvidar eso, la verdad."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:443
translate spanish hwb_s01_754a0a98:

    # "She whines once more and turns to me."
    "Ella gime una vez más y se vuelve hacia mí."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:447
translate spanish hwb_s01_afa37cca:

    # Girl "Hey, this might seem a little weird…"
    Girl "Слушай, это может показаться немного странным..."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:449
translate spanish hwb_s01_9d8a2c49:

    # "Oh no."
    "Oh no."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:453
translate spanish hwb_s01_90656792:

    # Girl "But could you take me somewhere nearby so I can get some gas?"
    Girl "Но не могла бы ты меня подбросить куда-нибудь, где можно достать немного бензина?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:455
translate spanish hwb_s01_342b2c07:

    # "And what do you know? She actually did it!"
    "¡Y mira tú por dónde, realmente lo hizo!"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:457
translate spanish hwb_s01_3dd9529a:

    # Amber "How long did you say you’ve been stuck out here?"
    Amber "И давно ты тут крутишься?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:461
translate spanish hwb_s01_37788455:

    # Girl "Hmm. I don’t know… A few hours maybe?"
    Girl "Хмм. Не знаю... Несколько часов, по-моему."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:465
translate spanish hwb_s01_7bc383e4:

    # Girl "I’ve been trying to wave down everyone who drives by, but you were the first to stop."
    Girl "Я пыталась тормознуть всех проезжающих, но ты первая, кто остановился."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:469
translate spanish hwb_s01_5f97b67c:

    # Amber "Hold on. {i}Everyone{/i}?"
    Amber "Подожди. {i}Всех{/i}?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:473
translate spanish hwb_s01_507afd43:

    # Girl "Yup!"
    Girl "Ага!"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:475
translate spanish hwb_s01_f55da67d:

    # "This heat must have her fried her brain. Does she have any idea how dangerous that is?"
    "Este calor debe haberle frito el cerebro. ¿Tiene idea de lo peligroso que es eso?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:479
translate spanish hwb_s01_f84a6ad4:

    # Amber "That’s probably not a good idea, you know."
    Amber "Вряд ли это хорошая идея, знаешь ли."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:483
translate spanish hwb_s01_0e67529b:

    # "She cocks her head to the side and gives me a look of genuine curiosity. Like it wasn’t obvious or something."
    "Inclina la cabeza hacia un lado y me mira con genuina curiosidad. Como si no fuera obvio o algo así."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:485
translate spanish hwb_s01_e363e7c5:

    # Girl "Huh, why?"
    Girl "Хм, почему?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:489
translate spanish hwb_s01_635fbfc9:

    # Amber "Well, you know…"
    Amber "Ну, знаешь..."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:497
translate spanish hwb_s01_93a3728f:

    # Amber "...because of the implication."
    Amber "...из-за последствий."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:501
translate spanish hwb_s01_9d6b3e31:

    # Girl "Uh, you used that word ‘implication.’ What implication?"
    Girl "Хм, “последствий”, говоришь. Каких последствий?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:505
translate spanish hwb_s01_ff1f9235:

    # Amber "You know, cute girl like you, out here in the desert."
    Amber "Ну, понимаешь, милая девушка вроде тебя, в пустыне."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:507
translate spanish hwb_s01_dbebc562:

    # Amber "Someone comes along, you're out here all alone."
    Amber "Кто-то подкатит, а ты здесь совсем одна."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:511
translate spanish hwb_s01_aa2ebe6c:

    # Amber "What are you going to do, say no?"
    Amber "Что ты будешь делать, скажешь “нет”?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:513
translate spanish hwb_s01_50febaf4:

    # Girl "It sounds like you're saying you're going to do something to me."
    Girl "Звучит так, как будто ты собираешься со мной что-то сделать..."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:517
translate spanish hwb_s01_28b4e404:

    # Amber "I'm not going to make you do anything. I just don't think you'll say no."
    Amber "Я тебе ничего не сделаю. Я просто не думаю, что ты скажешь “нет”."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:527
translate spanish hwb_s01_41817132:

    # Amber "You know, because of the implication."
    Amber "Ну, понимаешь, из-за... Последствий."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:531
translate spanish hwb_s01_4c02822c:

    # Girl "That sounds kind of dark."
    Girl "Звучит немного жутко."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:535
translate spanish hwb_s01_a846fe25:

    # Amber "You've got it all wrong, it's just..."
    Amber "Ты не поняла, просто..."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:537
translate spanish hwb_s01_bbcb63f2:

    # Amber "A cute, young girl alone in the middle of the desert—it’s just asking for trouble."
    Amber "Милая молодая девушка, одиноко стоящая на дороге в центре пустыни, просто напрашивается на неприятности."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:541
translate spanish hwb_s01_8456944c:

    # Girl "But you’re a cute, young girl alone in the middle of the desert."
    Girl "Но ведь и ты милая молодая девушка, которая одиноко стоит в центре пустыни."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:545
translate spanish hwb_s01_33598807:

    # Amber "Wh-What?"
    Amber "Ч-что?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:549
translate spanish hwb_s01_99a16b59:

    # "Her comeback takes me off guard and I turn away a little, avoiding eye contact."
    "Su respuesta me toma por sorpresa y me giro un poco, evitando el contacto visual."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:551
translate spanish hwb_s01_a6e6ff0b:

    # Amber "Yeah, but that’s different…"
    Amber "Да, но это другое..."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:555
translate spanish hwb_s01_2fbc2d27:

    # "A smile returns to her face, the same bright one that she showed me when I first pulled over."
    "Una sonrisa vuelve a su rostro, la misma brillante que me mostró cuando me detuve por primera vez."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:557
translate spanish hwb_s01_5695e60e:

    # "I’m still avoiding eye contact, but she leans over to the direction I’m looking and continues to smile."
    "Sigo evitando el contacto visual, pero ella se inclina hacia donde estoy mirando y continúa sonriendo."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:559
translate spanish hwb_s01_6a4e04e4:

    # Girl "So do you think you can give me a ride?"
    Girl "Так что, подбросишь меня?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:561
translate spanish hwb_s01_ea42957b:

    # Amber "I don’t know…"
    Amber "Я не знаю..."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:565
translate spanish hwb_s01_8e1c8a86:

    # Girl "Pleeeease. It shouldn’t take very long."
    Girl "Пожаааааааалуйста. Это не займет много времени."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:571
translate spanish hwb_s01_1778131e:

    # "This girl, it’s like she didn’t even listen to what I said."
    "Esta chica, es como si ni siquiera hubiera escuchado lo que dije."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:573
translate spanish hwb_s01_6caf1412:

    # "Still, better me than some psycho."
    "Aun así, mejor yo que algún psicópata."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:577
translate spanish hwb_s01_fcd2be31:

    # "Besides, it’s not like a small detour will make me late or anything."
    "Además, no es que un pequeño desvío me haga llegar tarde ni nada."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:579
translate spanish hwb_s01_aad0b7d6:

    # Amber "I guess it’s fine."
    Amber "Ладно, почему бы и нет."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:581
translate spanish hwb_s01_a2b56087:

    # Amber "I’m not in too big of a rush, anyway."
    Amber "Да и спешить-то мне особо некуда."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:587
translate spanish hwb_s01_95b07008:

    # Girl "Yay!"
    Girl "Ура!"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:621
translate spanish hwb_s01_028366ba:

    # "Before I’m even finished, she’s springing off the ground, bouncing to the motorhome."
    "Antes de que termine de hablar, ella ya está saltando del suelo, brincando hacia la casa rodante."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:627
translate spanish hwb_s01_b40a8a66:

    # Amber "Hey, wait!"
    Amber "Эй, подожди!"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:631
translate spanish hwb_s01_ce4248e6:

    # "But it’s already far too late, as she’s somehow made her way into the motorhome before its owner, even finding the time to give me a small wave from the passenger’s seat.."
    "Pero ya es demasiado tarde, porque de alguna manera se ha metido en la casa rodante antes que su dueña, incluso encontrando tiempo para saludarme con la mano desde el asiento del pasajero."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:639
translate spanish hwb_s01_72e72b77:

    # "I heave a heavy sigh, rubbing my temple as I climb back up into the driver’s seat."
    "Suelto un suspiro profundo, frotándome la sien mientras subo de nuevo al asiento del conductor."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:641
translate spanish hwb_s01_c759a869:

    # "The key is still dangling in the ignition. I wrench it around and the motorhome roars to life, forcing a surprised squeak out of the girl."
    "La llave aún cuelga del encendido. La giro y la casa rodante ruge al encender, arrancándole un chillido de sorpresa a la chica."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:679
translate spanish hwb_s01_6bd9f4a3:

    # Girl "By the way, my name is Marina. Thank you sooooo much for helping me out!"
    Girl "Кстати, меня зовут Марина. Большоооое тебе спасибо за помощь!"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:681
translate spanish hwb_s01_fb9876ba:

    # Amber "Amber. Don’t mention it."
    Amber "Эмбер. Не за что."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:694
translate spanish hwb_s01_29cef9ee:

    # "Careful not to hit her car, I back the RV up and turn it around, sending us in my original direction."
    "Con cuidado de no golpear su coche, retrocedo la RV y la giro, dirigiéndonos en mi dirección original."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:705
translate spanish hwb_s01_aa11d788:

    # "I put on my sunglasses and reach for the play button on the cassette player, finally giving in to temptation, but Marina starts up again."
    "Me pongo las gafas de sol y alcanzo el botón de reproducción del reproductor de casetes, cediendo por fin a la tentación, pero Marina vuelve a empezar."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:709
translate spanish hwb_s01_b8c68cdd:

    # Marina "Why aren’t we going the other way? Wasn’t there a station a little ways back?"
    Marina "А почему мы едем не в ту сторону? Там вроде бы совсем недалеко была заправка?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:711
translate spanish hwb_s01_e597c26e:

    # Amber "It was a bit more than a ‘little ways’ back."
    Amber "Она была гораздо дальше, чем “совсем недалеко”."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:713
translate spanish hwb_s01_3baf365e:

    # Amber "I saw a sign a few miles ago that said there was a station not too far from here, so we’re going there."
    Amber "Я видела знак в паре миль отсюда, на котором было написано про заправку чуть дальше по дороге, так что мы едем туда."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:717
translate spanish hwb_s01_e434fe44:

    # Marina "Oh wow, I didn’t even see that. You’re really observant!"
    Marina "Ого, я его даже не заметила. Ты такая внимательная!"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:719
translate spanish hwb_s01_43842884:

    # "Yeah, or you’re just really oblivious."
    "Sí, o simplemente eres muy despistada."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:721
translate spanish hwb_s01_5e9cdfdb:

    # Amber "Not really."
    Amber "Да не особо."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:725
translate spanish hwb_s01_e9693a20:

    # "Silence falls upon the motorhome, the roaring of the engine and swishing of the wind from outside being the only sounds."
    "El silencio cae sobre la casa rodante, siendo el rugido del motor y el silbido del viento del exterior los únicos sonidos."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:729
translate spanish hwb_s01_35a95a1e:

    # "I take that as my cue and reach for the cassette player once more, finally giv—"
    "Tomo eso como mi señal y alcanzo el reproductor de casetes una vez más, finalmen—"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:733
translate spanish hwb_s01_81351b4a:

    # Marina "How do you even drive this thing? It’s huuuuge!"
    Marina "Как ты вообще водишь эту штуку? Она же огроооооомная!"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:737
translate spanish hwb_s01_965bc190:

    # "Marina spreads her arms out like an eagle unfurling its wings, almost bopping me on the head in the process."
    "Marina extiende los brazos como un águila desplegando sus alas, casi golpeándome en la cabeza en el proceso."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:739
translate spanish hwb_s01_532cabfb:

    # "I clear my throat and grab her arm out from the air, gently placing it on her lap."
    "Me aclaro la garganta y agarro su brazo del aire, colocándolo suavemente en su regazo."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:741
translate spanish hwb_s01_bd37a4c7:

    # Amber "It’s not that bad. You get used to it."
    Amber "Это не так сложно. Привыкаешь."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:745
translate spanish hwb_s01_f4e66b31:

    # "She tilts her head to the side and gives a light grunt as if saying \"that so\" and we return to the silence of before."
    "Ella inclina la cabeza hacia un lado y emite un ligero gruñido como diciendo \"¿eso crees?\" y volvemos al silencio de antes."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:751
translate spanish hwb_s01_892f7753:

    # "Again, I reach for the cassette play—"
    "De nuevo, alcanzo el reproductor de case—"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:755
translate spanish hwb_s01_43926467:

    # Marina "So what are you doing out here? Are you going camping? Seems like what you’re doing is fun."
    Marina "А что ты тут делаешь? Ты собираешься в поход? Похоже, что это очень весело."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:759
translate spanish hwb_s01_e5d54073:

    # "I take a deep breath and hold it on as long as possible before letting it out."
    "Respiro hondo y aguanto el aire todo lo posible antes de soltarlo."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:761
translate spanish hwb_s01_ecdf9dc8:

    # Amber "Just traveling."
    Amber "Просто путешествую."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:768
translate spanish hwb_s01_59a5afec:

    # Amber "What about you? Why are you out here?"
    Amber "Ну, а ты? Ты почему здесь?"

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:772
translate spanish hwb_s01_3d2f338f:

    # Marina "Oh. Well... It’s kind of silly."
    Marina "Ох. Ну... Это такие глупости."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:774
translate spanish hwb_s01_8206a663:

    # "She scratches her head and lets out an embarrassed laugh before staring at her feet quieting down, and surprisingly enough, staying quiet. "
    "Se rasca la cabeza y suelta una risa avergonzada antes de mirar sus pies, callándose, y sorprendentemente, permaneciendo callada."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:778
translate spanish hwb_s01_11f53b4b:

    # "Well, looks like that worked."
    "Bueno, parece que funcionó."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:784
translate spanish hwb_s01_7a7b8d36:

    # "I reach for the cassette player one last time. I stop for a moment to look at the glove department and then Marina, who looks lost in thought, before finally pressing play."
    "Alcanzo el reproductor de casetes por última vez. Me detengo un momento para mirar la guantera y luego a Marina, que parece absorta en sus pensamientos, antes de presionar play."

translate spanish strings:

    # game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:4
    old "Girl"
    new "Девушка"


# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:159
translate spanish hwb_s01_22949cd9:

    # "I slam on the brakes, their shriek piercing my skull. A glance at my rearview mirror shows a girl cringing next to an ancient looking car, covering her ears as I screech down the road."
    "Piso los frenos, cuyo chirrido me perfora el cráneo. Un vistazo al espejo retrovisor muestra a una chica encogiéndose junto a un coche de aspecto antiguo, tapándose los oídos mientras chirrío carretera abajo."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:258
translate spanish hwb_s01_4f174c55:

    # "I almost feel embarrassed to be in front of someone who dresses so cutely, her frilly green top and skirt putting my red t-shirt and khakis to shame."
    "Casi me da vergüenza estar frente a alguien que se viste tan lindo, su blusa y falda verdes con volantes hacen que mi camiseta roja y mis caquis parezcan una pena."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:438
translate spanish hwb_s01_2012d16a:

    # "Seems like you'd have to be pretty absentminded to forget that, though."
    "Parece que tendrías que ser bastante distraída para olvidar eso, la verdad."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:534
translate spanish hwb_s01_3a32b1f4:

    # Amber "A cute, young girl alone in the middle of the desert... It’s just asking for trouble."
    Amber "Милая молодая девушка, одиноко стоящая на дороге в центре пустыни, просто напрашивается на неприятности."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:702
translate spanish hwb_s01_30ebc7e1:

    # "I reach for the play button on the cassette player, finally giving in to temptation, but Marina starts up again."
    "Alcanzo el botón de reproducción del reproductor de casetes, cediendo por fin a la tentación, pero Marina vuelve a empezar."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:708
translate spanish hwb_s01_c5bb3c52:

    # Amber "It was more than a ‘little ways’ back."
    Amber "Она была гораздо дальше, чем “совсем недалеко”."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:722
translate spanish hwb_s01_0079cdb2:

    # "Silence falls between us, the roaring of the engine and swishing of the wind from outside being the only sounds."
    "El silencio cae entre nosotras, siendo el rugido del motor y el silbido del viento del exterior los únicos sonidos."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:771
translate spanish hwb_s01_1002f30e:

    # "She scratches her head and lets out an embarrassed laugh before staring at her feet. She quiets down, and surprisingly, stays quiet. "
    "Se rasca la cabeza y suelta una risa avergonzada antes de mirar sus pies. Se calla, y sorprendentemente, permanece callada."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:781
translate spanish hwb_s01_f285558a:

    # "I reach for the cassette player one last time. I stop for a moment to look at the glove compartment and then Marina, who looks lost in thought."
    "Alcanzo el reproductor de casetes por última vez. Me detengo un momento para mirar la guantera y luego a Marina, que parece absorta en sus pensamientos."

# game/script/hwb_s01.rpy:783
translate spanish hwb_s01_df08e49f:

    # "Finally, I press play."
    pass

translate spanish strings:

    # script/hwb_s01.rpy:829
    old "Driving to the convenience store"
    new "Driving to the convenience store"

